{"bangumi":{"date":"2010-04-03","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/7d/62/4293_rqzH3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/7d/62/4293_rqzH3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/7d/62/4293_rqzH3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/7d/62/4293_rqzH3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/7d/62/4293_rqzH3.jpg"},"summary":"    满田拓也所著的棒球漫画「MAJOR(棒球大联盟)」，从1994年开始在「周刊少年Sunday」上连载至今，已经出版了74卷单行本，是「周刊少年 Sunday」里单行本卷数最多的长篇漫画。作品讲述了主人公・茂野吾郎，历经少棒联盟与高中棒球时代，进入美国大联盟挑战的成长历程。根据本作改编的 TV动画从2004年起在NHK教育电视台播放，自此基本每年都会推出一季，接续09年初的第5季的大联盟篇和世界杯篇，第6季已确定在2010年4月3 日播放。相比起其他热播中的长篇动画，「棒球大联盟」的分季制作相信更能让多数观众接受，一来可以忠实于原作漫画避免靠原创剧情拖时间，二来观众也不会因长期追看而产生视觉疲劳。","name":"メジャー 第6シリーズ","name_cn":"棒球大联盟 第六季","tags":[{"name":"棒球","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2010","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"棒球大联盟","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"体育","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"运动","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"森久保祥太郎","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SynergySP","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"major","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"森田成一","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2010年4月","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"草尾毅","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Sports","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"竞技","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"成长","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"笹本优子","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"福島利規","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"二周目","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"人生","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"カサヰケンイチ","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"森川智之","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"半年番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新番记录","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7.5","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"王道","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"i